beginning, containing an area of TWENTY EIGHT THOUSAND NINE HUNDRED EIGHTY FIVE (28,985) SQUARE METERS . All points referred to are indicated on the plan and are marked on the ground; P.S. cyl. conc. Mons. 15 x 60 cms.; bearings true; date of original survey, January 1906 ‑ February 1907, and that of the subdivision survey, July 18, 2000, and was approved on October 12, 2000.

IN WITNESS WHEREOF, I have hereunto set my hand and caused the seal of the Republic of the Philippines to be affixed.

Done in the City of Manila, this 1 st day of October, in the year of Our Lord, two thousand and one.

(Sgd.) GLORIA MACAPAGAL-ARROYO

By the President: (Sgd.) ALBERTO G. ROMULO Executive Secretary

